Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So these horns sprout on its host,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.89,0:01:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,when {\i1}Ah,{\i0} the mushi, eats silence\N and becomes a parasite?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes indeed, this is very rare...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And, what's that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:02:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A sake cup drawn by a boy with a God-like left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,His dislike for mushi-shi is well-known.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Come up with a better story than that, Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to force you to buy it, Dr. Adashino.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This item is too good for the likes\N of an ordinary collector.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let me have a close look...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be willing to sell it to you... if you'll help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.90,0:02:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,On my way here, I ran into something odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to capture it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Something odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard of what became of liquid mushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.73,0:02:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A "living swamp"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:49.69,EP Title BG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,0)\p1\blur1}m 0 0 l 950 0 950 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.89,0:02:49.69,EP Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,0)\be1}The Traveling Swamp
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As I was crossing the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I came across many swamps.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Another swamp...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But every time I went around one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.03,0:03:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...and looked back from the mountainside,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the swamp would be completely gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, after I had crossed the next mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,a new swamp would appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the foxes and badgers \Nare playing tricks on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you at the previous swamp, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know a shortcut through\N the mountains or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,For a moment, I doubted my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hair was so eerily green.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed dyed to its roots by the waters of the swamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something beyond here in that direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then can I ask you a question, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no ordinary swamp, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This swamp is... traveling...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,as it repeatedly comes up and \Nsinks down below the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:05:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you, I think it's trying to get\N beyond these mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A living swamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.19,0:05:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then are you moving together with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,if you go straight ahead, you'll come to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My destination is the fishing village there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you reach the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't be able to travel with the swamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to study the swamp water tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dark right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like a new type...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you wouldn't believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...when I said the swamp is traveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of my work, I'm open to most phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a mushi-shi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mushi-induced phenomena are all strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the {\i1}Suiko{\i0} for example. Liquid mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a clear and colorless liquid, but alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It prefers living in old water veins,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and sometimes stays in ponds and wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If one keeps drinking {\i1}Suiko,{\i0} mistakenly thinking it's water,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,he becomes unable to breathe without constant contact with water,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and his body begins turning transparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If left alone, he turns to liquid and flows away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the mushi itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it is gone by that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There are things like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So maybe a traveling swamp could exist, as well... You start to think like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you think it was creepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...never once thought it was frightening...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...since when I saw it for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it was so powerful and solemn...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Powerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It was swimming...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,at the bottom of the raging river...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I was swallowed by the currents,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And unable to make it to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw something huge and green...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...calmly rising from the bottom of the current...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When I came to, I was on the shores of the swamp in a mountain valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This color...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The swamp was actually the green\N thing that I saw earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,By then, my hair had become this color.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably had died once...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2100)}But the swamp said, "You may live."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why this swamp is the only place I feel I belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,At least...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...wear this when you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of it as becoming the bride of the water god.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us will look after your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name will become legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...as the honorable girl who saved\N our village from the flood...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If one keeps drinking it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,his body becomes transparent...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...and eventually flows away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's time to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going underground...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're leaving so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it wait a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I want to study it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for teaching me about many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to become part of this swamp now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I realize it earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That was what became of the {\i1}Suiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,After the {\i1}Suiko{\i0} disappeared from the well,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,it was traveling...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to become part of this swamp now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she realize what that means?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The swamp said, "You may live."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2850)}...wanted to live, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.91,0:12:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The swamp was... heading for the sea, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A swamp heading toward the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Know anything about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard something like that from an old fisherman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,at times, something "green", larger than a whale, comes down the river,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and once it reaches the sea, it dies as if it disintegrated into the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he never saw it himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but he said it's as though it \Nwere looking for a place to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we should hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging by the fact that the \Nfishermen aren't making a ruckus,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it hasn't reached the sea, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:52.30,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.1\move(1088,64,1350,64,25,4988)\frz1.678}Groundwater\N Tunnels
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a map of the underground\N water veins in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rare item.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was apparently based on dowsing rod vibrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it's reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:13:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When test wells were dug, \Nthe probability was fifty-fifty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The locations of the swamps I saw match this water vein.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So {\i1}Suiko{\i0} does move along the underground water veins...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But it forks here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't predict which way it's going like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Ginko,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I have this map, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a map of where the rivers may have been tens of thousands of years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Although the nearby river has its estuary in the same place as those times,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,it's interesting to see that it ran in quite different places back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to hear you \Nboasting about your collecti...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They match...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,These water veins were once a river.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When a river dries and gets buried underground,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it often remains as a layer of stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainwater seeps toward that layer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When a location where a river used\N to be is buried underground,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,it becomes a river for subterranean water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that swamp remembers \Nthis old river and is following it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,After deciding where to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like salmon, or sweetfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, it should eventually come to this estuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If it reaches the sea, there's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Adashino!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:26.48,Alt,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you gather some people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We're putting up a net near the estuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! That's it! Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We appreciate so many of you turning out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure it was okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem. We fishermen have all the time on our hands right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so few fish these days, \Nyou'd think the sea was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is a request from you, Dr. Adashino, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a doctor comes with perks, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's my wonderful personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Ginko,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't know if the girl can still\N be caught by this net, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, but it's our only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to save her so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you probably have a guilty conscience, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If the girl said she wanted \Ndesperately to live, I'd understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But she wanted to become part of the swamp, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That might be her happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes that's the way it is in this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,though it sounds cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,About that green sake cup...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It originally belonged to that young man's grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she was no longer either mushi or human, her only way to appear before the young man
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:16:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,was to restore that sake cup given to her by mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.91,0:16:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Although by doing so, she could never return to being human again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I made her mushi because that was what she wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not sure if that was for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Becoming mushi is different from a normal death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mushi exist between the living and the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They are "living", like people, and inanimate, like objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They're dead, but yet alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that's an unimaginable hell compared to "a moment of death"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The heart that makes one human is erased little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That was where she was headed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I saw her that final time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,she was wearing her finest kimono with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:17:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't many situations more cruel than that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I just heard something...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Slow it down! Don't lose the net!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stab it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a woman inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I-it slipped past...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a person... in a red kimono...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Were we... too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's up with this huge school of fish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko, they found the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,they said she looked like gelatin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How's the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the seawater washed out that green stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she's like dough now I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The fish are gathering to feed \Non the carcass of that green stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The ocean is black with fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's me take a look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl brought a wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When we reached the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.14,0:20:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell... the swamp... was dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so... so terrified of dissolving into the swamp...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so sad about the swamp dying...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It lived for tens of thousands of years, if not more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You accompanied it on its final journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You were fortunate to have met it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there, Io.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Adashino...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, looks like another large catch today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:21:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, fish are coming from far away, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They grow this big by feeding on the swamp's carcass.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hair's jet black now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, so I can't breathe underwater anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to live independently here by the sea where the swamp died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Swamps again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.34,0:21:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.34,0:21:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason it surfaced...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...was to create its offspring, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Swamps are born and eventually become stagnant...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.19,0:21:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When the world nurtured in their bosom comes to an end,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.99,0:21:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they put on their own feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:22:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and begin to move...
